  <!-- COMMON JOBS -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:#f8fafc;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Common Emergencies We Fix Across St Helens</h2>
      <p class="pf-sub">The plumbing faults we attend most frequently across WA10, WA11, WA12 and surrounding areas.</p>
      <div class="jobs-grid" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Burst Pipes and Water Through the Ceiling</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£120 to £350</span><span class="job-time">30 to 90 mins</span></div><p>Particularly common in WA10 Victorian terraces where loft tanks and external pipework have never been properly insulated. We stop the leak, repair or replace the affected section and check for hidden water damage before we leave your St Helens property.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>No Hot Water and Boiler Breakdown</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£150 to £500</span><span class="job-time">45 to 120 mins</span></div><p>From ageing back boilers in WA10 terraces to modern condensing units in Newton-le-Willows, we diagnose and repair on the same visit. 95% of St Helens boiler call-outs resolved on the first visit with parts from the van. Gas Safe engineers only.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Blocked Toilets and Drains</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£80 to £250</span><span class="job-time">30 to 90 mins</span></div><p>Stop flushing and call us. Victorian clay drainage across WA10 is prone to root ingress and scale. We use professional clearing equipment on every drain blockage job. Most St Helens drain blockages are cleared on the same visit.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card job-card--warning"><h3>Gas Leaks</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">FREE safety visit</span><span class="job-time">Priority response</span></div><p>If you smell gas, get out and call <a href="https://cadentgas.com/gas-escapes" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="font-weight:700;">Cadent Gas on 0800 111 999</a> first. Then call us. Gas safety make-safe visit is FREE. Gas Safe registered engineers only on all gas work across St Helens.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Major Leaks</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£80 to £200</span><span class="job-time">20 to 60 mins</span></div><p>Leaking radiators, pipes under sinks, toilet cistern failures and valve issues. We identify the source quickly and repair or replace the component before it causes water damage. Most major leak call-outs in St Helens resolved within 60 minutes.</p></div>
        <div class="job-card"><h3>Heating Failure</h3><div class="job-meta"><span class="job-price">£120 to £350</span><span class="job-time">60 to 120 mins</span></div><p>Heating failing is a priority during cold months. We check pump, motorised valves, thermostats and pipework on every heating call-out across St Helens. Priority response for elderly and vulnerable occupants in WA10, WA11 and WA12.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


