          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Boiler Service St Helens</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">Annual boiler service £120. Gas Safe engineer. Benchmark updated. Certificate same day.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/gas-safety-certificate-st-helens" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Gas Safety Certificates St Helens</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">CP12 landlord certificates from £80. Same-day available. Combined with service for £175.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/power-flushing-st-helens" class="service-card" style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;flex-direction:column;">
          <strong style="color:var(--navy);">Power Flushing St Helens</strong>
          <span style="color:var(--text);flex:1;">Cold radiators or noisy boiler? Power flush from £350. Warranty protection included.</span>
          <span style="display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--orange);font-weight:700;font-size:0.88rem;">View service &rarr;</span>
        </a>
