          <h3 style="font-size:1.1rem;margin:0.75rem 0 0.4rem;text-align:center;">Is ECO4 funding available for St Helens homeowners?</h3>
          <p>Yes. The ECO4 government scheme funds boiler replacements and heating upgrades for eligible households including those on certain benefits and low income properties. St Helens has a high proportion of eligible properties across WA10 and WA9. We can assess your eligibility and manage the application process as part of a new boiler or central heating installation. See our <a href="/central-heating-installation-st-helens">central heating St Helens page</a> for more detail.</p>
